{"sections":{"main":{"type":"main-page","settings":{"padding_top":28,"padding_bottom":28}},"image_banner_Hm8tGA":{"type":"image-banner","name":"t:sections.image-banner.presets.name","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/bagamati.jpg","image_overlay_opacity":0,"image_height":"medium","image_behavior":"none","desktop_content_position":"middle-center","desktop_content_alignment":"center","show_text_box":false,"color_scheme":"","stack_images_on_mobile":true,"mobile_content_alignment":"center","show_text_below":true}},"rich_text_tEM86M":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"heading_LLjLzg":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Traditional Craftsmanship meets Modern Design","heading_size":"h2"}},"text_JxJwL9":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>アジアの豊かな自然の中で育まれた天然素材を使用し、自社工場で一つひとつ丁寧に作り上げられる「The Bagmati（バグマティ）」。古くから伝わる伝統的な技法を守りながら、現代のライフスタイルに寄り添うデザインを追求しています。手作業だからこそ生まれる、一つひとつ異なる表情や温かみをお楽しみください。<\/p><p><\/p>"}},"button_PrmcNP":{"type":"button","disabled":true,"settings":{"button_label":"ボタンのラベル","button_link":"","button_style_secondary":false,"button_label_2":"","button_link_2":"","button_style_secondary_2":false}}},"block_order":["heading_LLjLzg","text_JxJwL9","button_PrmcNP"],"name":"t:sections.rich-text.presets.name","settings":{"desktop_content_position":"center","content_alignment":"center","color_scheme":"","full_width":true,"padding_top":40,"padding_bottom":40}},"image_with_text_4n3JGd":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"heading_PEnTJV":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"熟練した職人による手編み","heading_size":"h2"}},"text_dDx69B":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>複雑な編みのパターンや繊細なシルエットは、熟練した職人たちの手によって生み出されます。大量生産にはない、手仕事ならではの強さとしなやかさが、使うほどに愛着を深めてくれます。<\/p>","text_style":"body"}},"button_p4Gx9z":{"type":"button","disabled":true,"settings":{"button_label":"ボタンのラベル","button_link":"","button_style_secondary":false}}},"block_order":["heading_PEnTJV","text_dDx69B","button_p4Gx9z"],"name":"t:sections.image-with-text.presets.name","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/BAGMATI.jpg","height":"adapt","desktop_image_width":"medium","layout":"image_first","image_behavior":"none","content_layout":"no-overlap","desktop_content_position":"top","desktop_content_alignment":"left","mobile_content_alignment":"left","section_color_scheme":"","color_scheme":"","padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":0}},"image_with_text_dnaj7J":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"heading_HNnKx7":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"自然の恵みと、厳選された素材","heading_size":"h2"}},"text_wPyfkW":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>使うほどに味わいが増す天然素材と、現代的なエッセンスの組み合わせ。その調和が、日常の装いにさりげない上質さを添えてくれます。素材の持つ本来の風合いを大切にするのが、私たちのこだわりです。<\/p>","text_style":"body"}},"button_wjtbLU":{"type":"button","disabled":true,"settings":{"button_label":"ボタンのラベル","button_link":"","button_style_secondary":false}}},"block_order":["heading_HNnKx7","text_wPyfkW","button_wjtbLU"],"name":"t:sections.image-with-text.presets.name","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/1_5eab5d69-25ed-4021-ae4c-efde11760769.jpg","height":"adapt","desktop_image_width":"medium","layout":"image_first","image_behavior":"none","content_layout":"no-overlap","desktop_content_position":"top","desktop_content_alignment":"left","mobile_content_alignment":"left","section_color_scheme":"","color_scheme":"","padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":0}},"rich_text_GQHgpV":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"heading_T79kGc":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"","heading_size":"h1"}},"text_eHmWNh":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":""}},"button_DXDVtp":{"type":"button","settings":{"button_label":"The Bagmati の商品を見る","button_link":"shopify:\/\/collections","button_style_secondary":false,"button_label_2":"","button_link_2":"","button_style_secondary_2":false}}},"block_order":["heading_T79kGc","text_eHmWNh","button_DXDVtp"],"name":"t:sections.rich-text.presets.name","settings":{"desktop_content_position":"center","content_alignment":"center","color_scheme":"","full_width":true,"padding_top":40,"padding_bottom":52}}},"order":["main","image